Problem: Length of Last Word
Topic: Strings
Difficulty: Easy

Approach:
Traverse the string from the end, skip trailing spaces, then count characters until the next space or beginning of the string is reached.

Time Complexity: O(n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

Code:
class Solution {
public:
    int lengthOfLastWord(string s) {
        //we have to consider about spaces too
        int i= s.size()-1;   //i==for last string
        int len=0;
        while(i>=0 && s[i]==' '){
            i--;
        }
        while(i>=0 && s[i]!=' '){
            len++;
            i--;
        }        
        return len;
    }
};
